Mint Music Artist Social Media Network allows musicians, vocalist, bands & labels to freely market and network on an independent music industry site. Mint Music Network as created to help music artists enhance their brand and elevate their skill set through the spirit of competition. Signed, unsigned, global or local, MintMusic.com can provide you with the online visibility that's needed to be seen globally by record execs, A&R's, talent scouts, etc.

Working for others suck, this app helps liberate artist from the likes of cubicles, paper hats, out of offices, punch ins, etc.  Mint Music provides independent artists true independence; such as independence from their parents basement and from their friends couch. Fans can support music artists by downloading and listening to the MintP3 and Mint Music Radio. Independent artists join Mint Music to support themselves. Vendors & venues join to get FREE radio advertising on MMR. Downloading MM also keeps me gainfully unemployed, Bosses Suck. http://www.MintMusic.com http://www.MintMusicRadio.com
